extendedInfo.description: Optimized For Slow Internet !Going to Nehru Place to buy IT product? Don't know where to start? Then this app is for you.Get this FREE price list about the all IT products like Hard Disk,Processor, MotherBoard, etc. and computer peripherals on your device JUST A CLICK away. This app will provide you the price range of the product you have been searching.Why you need this app?Every one needs to have an idea of latest and updated cost or price list of an item before purchasing or procuring it. Some times it is very tough for an individual to visit the Nehru Place market or some other computer hardware shop physically for getting these price List ideas before making a purchase, then in such cases this application is helpful where you can get the idea of Nehru Place market price list by just browsing it and without actually visiting the market.Disclaimer: These prices are not specified to any particular store or market place , prices may vary according to daily market changes . The developer is not responsible in case you are following prices for a particular store .These prices are general prices for the time being and to give an idea how much would be the product cost in the market of Nehru Place .market , computer parts , hardware , software , cost , rate , price , graphics card , cabinet , mouse . keyboard , laptop prices, cooling fan ,cost to cost motherboard asus gigabit msi , desi , indian market, charger .
